    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克加入交流，转向全天交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/nasdaq-joins-exchanges-seeking-to-offer-round-the-clock-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克公司（NASDAQ Inc.）计划在其股票交易所提供24小时交易，这是最新的地点，旨在利用不断增长的美国股票需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/nasdaq-joins-exchanges-seeking-to-offer-round-the-clock-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
